                            <div class="mt-6">
                                            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold leading-8 md:text-xl md:font-bold md:leading-7 text-gray-800">
                            Job summary
                        </h3>
                        <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-5 md:text-base md:leading-6 text-gray-500 font-normal">
                            We are seeking enthusiastic and motivated Sales and Marketing Personnel to help us connect with new clients and expand our business. In this role, you will be responsible for identifying potential clients, promoting our services, and closing deals to grow our client base.
                        </p>
